These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-1::.
There 7 different types of food: apple, apricot, kiwi, pineapple, radish, raspberry, spinach
7 different pets are kept: mouse, hedgehog, chinchilla, dog, frog, rabbit, fish
 1. the person eating kiwi is on the far left##1
 2. the person eating pineapple is not the owner of the rabbit##6
 3. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the person eating apricot##1
 4. the owner of the fish is somewhere to the right of the owner of the frog##5
 5. the person eating radish is on the left or right of the person eating spinach##3
 6. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1
 7. the person eating raspberry is somewhere between the person eating apricot and the owner of the hedgehog##7
 8. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
 9. the owner of the dog is somewhere between the person eating radish and the owner of the chinchilla##7
10. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the owner of the mouse##3
11. the owner of the frog is on the far left##1
12. the person eating pineapple is somewhere to the left of the owner of the fish##5
13. the person eating pineapple is somewhere to the right of the person eating raspberry##5
14. the person eating spinach is somewhere to the right of the person eating radish##5
15. the person eating radish is the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4     |     5     |     6     |    7    |
| Food          | kiwi    | apple    | apricot | raspberry | pineapple | radish    | spinach |
| Pet   | frog | mouse | chinchilla  | rabbit   | dog    | hedgehog | fish |

