.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-2::.
House: farmhouse, townhouse, cape-cod, modern, futuristic, art-deco, colonial
The people have 7 different hobbies: camping, chess, gardening, hiking, rock-climbing, singing, skydiving
 1. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere between the colonial house and the townhouse house##7
 2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the modern house##1
 3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the art-deco house##1
 5. the farmhouse house is somewhere between the person who's hobby is hiking and the person who's hobby is chess##7
 6. the art-deco house is somewhere between the modern house and the person who's hobby is gardening##7
 7. the futuristic house is somewhere between the modern house and the townhouse house##7
 8. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 9. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere to the left of the futuristic house##5
10. the futuristic house is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is singing##5
11. the person who's hobby is singing is not the colonial house##6
12. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
13. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is between the person who's hobby is hiking and the modern house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |       5       |      6      |    7    |
| House    | colonial  | cape-cod | art-deco | modern | farmhouse     | futuristic | townhouse  |
| Hobby   | gardening | singing | chess  | skydiving  | rock-climbing | hiking      | camping |

