.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-3::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: cooking, filmmaking, rock-climbing, skydiving, sudoku, traveling, video-games
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, tiparillo, blend, cain, vegafina, ritmeester, swisher
 1. the swisher-smoker is between the person who's hobby is rock-climbing and the blend-smoker##2
 2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere to the right of the tiparillo-smoker##5
 3. the tiparillo-smoker is not the person who's hobby is skydiving##6
 4. the bongani-smoker is somewhere to the right of the ritmeester-smoker##5
 5. the bongani-smoker is between the ritmeester-smoker and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2
 6. the blend-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##5
 7. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far right##1
 8. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left or right of the cain-smoker##3
 9. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere between the vegafina-smoker and the swisher-smoker##7
10. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##3
11. the person who's hobby is sudoku is in an even position##4
12. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not the bongani-smoker##6
13. the person who's hobby is traveling is somewhere between the person who's hobby is filmmaking and the person who's hobby is sudoku##7
14. the cain-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##3
15. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##3
16. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not the ritmeester-smoker##6
17. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left or right of the blend-smoker##3
18. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
19. the bongani-smoker is somewhere to the left of the vegafina-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3     |    4    |       5       |     6     |      7      |
| Hobby         | cooking | filmmaking | traveling | sudoku  | rock-climbing | skydiving | video-games |
| Cigar   | tiparillo   | ritmeester       | bongani   | vegafina | cain           | swisher     | blend     |

