.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-4::.
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: golf, lacrosse, parkour, soy-milking, skiing, tennis, volleyball
There are 7 different favourite beverages: sprite, 7up, water, soy-milk, cola, tea, juice
 1. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the right of the person drinking 7up##5
 2. the person who's sport is parkour is in an odd position##4
 3. the person who's sport is skiing is somewhere to the left of the person drinking juice##5
 4. the person who's sport is skiing is somewhere to the right of the person drinking tea##5
 5. the person who's sport is soy-milking is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##5
 6. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
 7. the person drinking water is somewhere between the person drinking 7up and the person drinking cola##7
 8. the person who's sport is soy-milking is on the far left##1
 9. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is golf##5
10. the person who's sport is tennis is in an even position##4
11. the person who's sport is tennis is somewhere between the person who's sport is skiing and the person who's sport is lacrosse##7
12. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##5
13. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
14. the person who's sport is parkour is somewhere to the left of the person drinking juice##5
15. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
16. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the left of the person drinking water##5
17. the person drinking soy-milk is between the person who's sport is tennis and the person drinking tea##2
18. the person who's sport is skiing is not the person drinking juice##6
19. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the right of the person drinking 7up##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |    2    |     3     |     4      |     5      |    6    |    7     |
| Sport       | soy-milking | golf    | parkour   | volleyball | skiing     | tennis  | lacrosse |
| Beverage   | cola    | water | 7up | tea      | soy-milk | sprite | juice      |

