 2. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere between the owner of the cat and the owner of the hamster##7
 3. the pall-mall-smoker is on the far left##1
 4. the owner of the horse is not the pall-mall-smoker##6
 5. the owner of the horse is somewhere to the left of the owner of the cat##5
 6. the blend-smoker is somewhere to the left of the bongani-smoker##5
 7. the bongani-smoker is somewhere to the left of the prince-smoker##5
 8. the owner of the cat is somewhere to the left of the owner of the turtle##5
 9. the owner of the rabbit is not the bongani-smoker##6
10. the blend-smoker is somewhere to the left of the owner of the horse##5
11. the bongani-smoker is somewhere to the left of the old-henry-smoker##5
12. the prince-smoker is the owner of the lizard##1
13. the blend-smoker is on the right of the pall-mall-smoker##1
14. the blend-smoker is the owner of the ferret##1
15. the prince-smoker is on the left of the oliveros-smoker##1
16. the old-henry-smoker is on the left of the bluemaster-smoker##1

