.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-6::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: juice, milk, hot-chocolate, water, iced-tea, mirinda, cola
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: basketball, biathlon, skateboarding, snowboarding, soccer, surfing, weightlifting
 1. the person drinking milk is in the middle##1
 2. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##5
 3. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking water##1
 4. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person drinking milk##7
 5. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
 6. the person drinking juice is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 7. the person who's sport is surfing is somewhere to the left of the person drinking cola##5
 8. the person who's sport is basketball is not the person drinking juice##6
 9. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##5
10. the person who's sport is snowboarding is not the person drinking juice##6
11. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left or right of the person who's sport is biathlon##3
12. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person who's sport is soccer##3
13. the person drinking milk is not the person who's sport is biathlon##6
14. the person drinking cola is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
15. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere to the right of the person drinking cola##5
16. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
17. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |       2       |    3    |    4    |      5       |    6     |     7      |
| Beverage   | juice    | iced-tea      | water  | milk | cola         | mirinda | hot-chocolate      |
