.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-8::.
There 7 different types of food: blueberry, lemon, mango, pomegranate, raspberry, strawberry, zucchini
7 different games are played: backgammon, go, domino, chess, billiard, monopoly, snooker
 1. the person eating zucchini is not the person playing snooker##6
 2. the person eating strawberry is somewhere to the left of the person playing go##5
 3. the person eating strawberry is on the left or right of the person eating raspberry##3
 4. the person eating strawberry is the person eating strawberry##1
 5. the person playing go is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
 6. the person playing billiard is somewhere between the person playing domino and the person playing backgammon##7
 7. the person eating lemon is in an odd position##4
 8. the person playing backgammon is in an even position##4
 9. the person eating mango is the person playing chess##1
10. the person eating strawberry is between the person eating raspberry and the person playing billiard##2
11. the person eating blueberry is on the left or right of the person playing backgammon##3
12. the person playing billiard is in the middle##1
13. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the person playing domino##1
14. the person eating pomegranate is on the left or right of the person eating strawberry##3
15. the person eating mango is on the far left##1
16. the person eating mango is somewhere to the left of the person playing snooker##5
17. the person eating blueberry is somewhere to the right of the person playing backgammon##5
18. the person playing domino is somewhere to the right of the person eating zucchini##5

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1   |    2     |     3     |      4      |     5      |     6      |    7    |
| Food   | mango | zucchini | blueberry | pomegranate | strawberry | raspberry  | lemon   |
| Game    | chess  | backgammon      | snooker      | billiard    | domino       | go | monopoly |

