 7. the person watching adventure movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching romance movies##5
 8. the person driving the snowmobile is the person watching comedy movies##1
 9. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere to the right of the person driving the roller##5
10. the person driving the train is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1
